Uses of Class
org.oucs.gaboto.entities.GabotoEntity

Packages that use GabotoEntity
org.oucs.gaboto.entities GabotoEntitys are java representations of objects from the Gaboto ontology. 
org.oucs.gaboto.entities.pool GabotoEntityPools are collections of GabotoEntitys. 
org.oucs.gaboto.entities.pool.filters Contains interfaces and implementations of filters to guide the creation process of GabotoEntityPools. 
org.oucs.gaboto.entities.time While GabotoEntitys are representation of Gaboto objects at a specific point in time, GabotoTimeBasedEntity represent an Gaboto object over its lifespan. 
org.oucs.gaboto.entities.utils This package contains Annotations used to mark up the get and set methods of GabotoEntitys and several helper methods to work with GabotoEntity. 
org.oucs.gaboto.exceptions Contains various exceptions that are used in the Gaboto system. 
org.oucs.gaboto.model Contains the classes implementing the data model. 
org.oucs.gaboto.util Contains various utility classes.
